~ start
Placa: [b]--- ESQUEMA DE CONTROLOS ---[/b]
Placa: [b]Movimento:[/b] W, A, S, D / Analógico Esquerdo
Placa: [b]Ataque:[/b] Espaço / Clique Esquerdo / R1
Placa: [b]Esquiva (Dash):[/b] Shift Esquerdo / Clique Direito / L1
Placa: [b]Transformar (Humano <-> Spork):[/b] Q / Triângulo (Δ)
Placa: [b]Interagir / Aceitar:[/b] E / Quadrado (⬜) / Cross (X)
Placa: [b]Inventário:[/b] I / Touchpad
Placa: [b]Pausa / Retroceder:[/b] Esc / Botão Menu (三) / Círculo (O)
=> END

~ game_start
Chef: Ugh... My head...
Chef: Where am I? Am I holding a Spork? It feels strange somehow.
Chef: Oh right, I'm still in this godforsaken dungeon...
Chef: Where I lost the rest of my party and somehow ended up in... a sacrifice room?
Spork: More like a prison, if you ask me.
Chef: Well, no one asked y-
Chef: Wait, who said that?
Chef: ...
Chef: Oh God, I'm finally going insane... and kinda hungry.
Chef: I should eat one of the emergency rations I've brought with me.
=> END

~ first_food
Chef: Usually a bite like this makes me instantly full, but I've eaten the whole thing and I'm still hungry...
Spork: Me too, maybe you should try eating the rest!
Chef: Gah! I need to get out of here now! [WASD to move]
=> END

~ pit_dialogue
Spork: Falling in those pits would be quite painful... I can give you a hand if that happens!
Chef: There will be, little weird voice in my head, no need for that. I dont plan on falling anyway!
Chef: I should be careful where I step here, the bridges seem to have collapsed... And I can't even see the bottom of this pit.
=> END

~ key_obtained
You got a key! Wonder what it's for...
=> END

~ lever
Something happened in this room.
=> END

~ boss
This door is locked.
if GameManager.has_key:
	Unlocked with the key from the mimic.
	set GameManager.boss_unlocked = true
else:
	There must be a key somewhere in this floor.
=> END